    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b052241eb4d91257964beb88fe45952c.avif?t=1765893039\" width=1560 height=648 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《地下城骑士团》是一款以 D&amp;D 为主题的战略型动作 RPG 游戏。</strong><br>在以经典奇幻构建的世界观中，玩家将利用武器、魔法、神器与道具组建队伍，对抗威胁世界的巨大 Boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/1128757122e22c3d66813f826474507d.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>战斗</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除操作角色外，其余角色将自动行动。<br>通过受 CRPG 启发的<strong>战术指令（时间暂停）功能</strong>，可以暂时停止战斗，并根据情况调整战略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，还能实时切换操作角色。<br>亲手操控战士的嘲讽、法师的流星召唤、盗贼的后跳、牧师的治疗，将其组合成强力连击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/d0b99d521e1dfed3aef9bdac6d715a63.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/d0b99d521e1dfed3aef9bdac6d715a63.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/d0b99d521e1dfed3aef9bdac6d715a63.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>队伍组成</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可从 9 个职业中选择 4 名角色组建队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个职业都有坦克、输出、辅助等基本定位，并可通过升级属性与进阶职业获得更强的角色定位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合从装备中获得的特性，以及能调整队伍站位的<strong>阵型系统</strong>，玩家能够实现自己构想的战术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/53d2c29df2e086797752ad4ff6f0cf81.avif?t=1765893039\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>成长路线</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有队员都能以多种方式成长：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进阶职业转职</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取特性</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精通强化</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备制作与合成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备强化</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现角色之间的羁绊</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过多种途径，角色将不断迈向无尽的成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.poster.avif?t=1765893039\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.webm?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072980/extras/b62e92b6cce253638caf1a2984ce05cf.mp4?t=1765893039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>无尽的游戏循环</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与强大的 Boss 展开类突袭的战斗。<br>瞄准并破坏 Boss 的弱点，获取素材来制作装备。<br>尤其是在怪物进入硬直状态时，结合战略与操作的协同作用，可以造成爆发性伤害并将其击败。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>本地多人</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 通过离线双人模式，与好友一起研究强力的技能连携。</p>",
